🚨 𝐎𝐅𝐅𝐈𝐂𝐈𝐀𝐋: Chelsea sign Liam Delap on £30m deal from Ipswich and contract until 2031 💙🚜

“Growing up watching this club, I understand stature of it and also how incredible it has been over the years”.

“I 𝐰𝐚𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐝 𝐭𝐨 𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐨 𝐂𝐡𝐞𝐥𝐬𝐞𝐚 𝐭𝐨 𝐰𝐢𝐧 𝐭𝐫𝐨𝐩𝐡𝐢𝐞𝐬… when I spoke to the club, everyone wanted to get back to the very top with desire to keep adding trophies, take the club back to where it belongs, that’s main objective”.
